window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Hitched</i> is a dark gray<b> </b>hitchhiker romance. All of the Ride or Die romances are standalone,<b> </b>and can be listened to in any order!</p> <p>The rabbit's foot sways in the car, a bad omen that I choose to ignore. Her innocent face and offer for a ride are too tempting. Little does she know that I'm a dangerous man on the run, a sociopath with a thirst for the thrill of the hunt. Selena is my rabbit, and I'm about to ensnare her in my trap. As we speed toward the border, emotions I thought I was incapable of stir within me. But danger lurks around every turn, and the stakes rise with each passing moment. What will happen when we reach our destination? Will I let her go, or will I keep her by my side forever? The game has just begun, rabbit. Are you ready to play?</p> <p>Buckle up for a heart-pounding ride with <i>Hitched</i>, the dark hitchhiker romance that will leave you begging for more.</p> <p>Note: This dark hitchhiker romance has extreme content. Full list of content warnings on the author's website. Please listen responsibly!</p>"; 
